Name: Tactical Operations Force
About the game: Tactical Operations Force - TOF is a Third Person Shooter Game that allow players to play up to 10 vs 10 matches over the internet on Steam. Main Game features are: Multiplayer System LAN Multiplayer System Single Player Players are able to buy weapons with gamecoins that are obtained playing the game. The game have 4 different modes: Conquest Rush Team DeathMatch DeathMatch Game is under development and currently we are in Beta Stage, we are going to include more weapons, customization options and more maps in the near future.
Developers: Leonardo Andres Villegas Alegre,Othman Power Switch,Rajan Rana
